---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';

const brands = ["Titleist", "FootJoy", "Nike Golf", "Bridgestone", "Cleveland", "BlueTees", "Under Armour"];
const resellerBrands = ["TaylorMade", "Callaway", "Cobra", "Mizuno", "PING"];
---

<BaseLayout title="Pro Shop" description="The ALCC Pro Shop — official retailer for Titleist, FootJoy, Nike Golf, and more.">
  <PageHero title="Pro Shop" subtitle="Formerly the Pin Seekers Bar room — now home to the club's fully stocked Pro Shop." />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p>In 2014, the idea began as a simple concept: transforming the
      former men's locker room at ALCC into a gathering spot. Members
      wanted a place that offered easier access, great views of the first
      tee, and a relaxed atmosphere for enjoying the 19th hole after a
      round.</p>

      <p>The project was financed and completed almost entirely by
      members, who replaced nearly 100 lockers, a shower area, an office
      lounge, and storage space with a comfortable room filled with tables,
      chairs, barstools — and most importantly, a well-stocked bar.</p>

      <p>A few years later, as the original Pro Shop began to show its age,
      management relocated it into the Pin Seekers Bar room and added a
      manager's office. Today, the space continues to evolve: golfers
      enjoy a deck overlooking the putting green and first tee, along with
      a fully stocked Pro Shop featuring many of today's top brands.</p>

      <h2>Official Retailer For</h2>
      <ul>
        {brands.map((b) => <li>{b}</li>)}
      </ul>
      <p>Additional partnerships through local resellers provide {resellerBrands.join(', ')}.</p>

      <p>If you'd like to order equipment, contact the pro shop with your
      information and they'll provide a price quote.</p>

      <a class="btn btn--red" href="tel:18145424343">Call the Pro Shop</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
